Author: j4jackj
Text: I know over Twitter somebody whose only restriction is on carbs (because she's a total headcase and finds she is less of one on no carbs). She obsessively logs and weighs everything (so she can know from one day to the next what any given intervention is doing to her appetite and energy), but doesn't deliberately restrict her calories. She's quite narrow, so to speak, but I've not seen Tay's '89 tour pics, so maybe Tay was thinner.
